{"tid":1472181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［文宣炸彈整合］ 疑似大陸執法人員混入香港警察 (更新版)","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:14:12.000Z","uid":89898,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"61b59a027257e34ef86dc7c1e2d00679a949c77d","tid":1472181,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點1：</span></span>6月12日，記者同議員要求一班疑似警員出示委任證，儘管佢地當時乜都冇做過（即係就算公開警員編號都唔會畀人投訴乜乜乜），但係佢地都冇出示，淨係得個十問九唔應、近乎聽唔明廣東話嘅奇怪態度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7ORvzSJ2OGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7ORvzSJ2OGI&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=c93829d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7ORvzSJ2OGI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PyWr52Vqiog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPyWr52Vqiog&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=70394d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PyWr52Vqiog</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點2：</span></span>6月12日，部分速龍小隊所著嘅鞋款奇怪而不統一，有手足搵到其中一款嘅型號。有藍底FB Page解釋係SDU所著鞋款，但係可信性成疑，而且都解釋唔到圖一兩款鞋嘅唔同。呢點要多啲熟軍事用品嘅朋友了解吓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4hr6AD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4hr6AD.png&h=df5b5fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D56o8OY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD56o8OY.jpg&h=1fa385e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q7h0rAD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7h0rAD.jpg&h=c862d280&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《關於612我有個問題想問好耐...》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241537/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241537/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點3：</span></span>6 月12日，當時尚未發展到全面嘅仇警情緒，但係已經有警員對傳媒工作者態度極度異常，似乎唔習慣香港嘅新聞採訪自由。事例包括有蘋果記者出示記者證要求穿越警方防線，但有警員反駁只係「員工卡」，而非「記者證」；晚上清場冇人，仍然對記者林彥邦諸多阻撓，及後佢喺blog回應「對其實，這類採訪經歷，在深圳河以北見慣見熟&hellip;」，似乎別有所指。<br />\n<br />\n《【引渡惡法】軍裝警唔識分記者證 民權觀察促「速龍小隊」展示警員編號》<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190614/59715650?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59715650%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=f9de9efa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59715650%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b09bca44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190614/59715650?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n《清場時不斷喝罵、無理對待記者的警察》<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/120484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F120484&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=7b9e39d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/120484</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點4：</span></span>7月31日，有美方高級官員表示有中國部隊集結喺香港境域附近，動機不明。然而，觀乎近日諸多證據，顯示香港警隊已被大陸執法人員混入，有可能同當時嘅集結相關。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博：解放軍或武警在香港的邊境地區集結》<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471657-20190731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471657-20190731.htm&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=56c7b08c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471657-20190731.htm&h=694918ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471657-20190731.htm</a><br />\n《White House Official Says Chinese Forces Are on Hong Kong&rsquo;s Border》<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2019-07-31/white-house-official-says-chinese-forces-are-on-hong-kong-s-border-video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2F2019-07-31%2Fwhite-house-official-says-chinese-forces-are-on-hong-kong-s-border-video&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=a6f98924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2019-07-31/white-house-official-says-chinese-forces-are-on-hong-kong-s-border-video</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點5：</span></span>8月4日，銅鑼灣清場行動，FFTV現場live見證一大群疑似防暴猛攻前方，無視指揮官命令狂放催淚彈，同時亦聽到有分辨唔到係咪用普通話講嘅「後退後退」(0:07)。及後8月7日凌晨深水埗，亦有前線疑似警員失控向前跑、無視「停呀停呀」嘅指令，要後面白衫跑上去阻止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FTVV612/videos/2504915106238077/?t=33\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFTVV612%2Fvideos%2F2504915106238077%2F%3Ft%3D33&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=8c5216c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FTVV612/videos/2504915106238077/?t=33</a><br />\n《【逆權運動】深水埗警員離群失控狂跑 上司揮棍阻止：停呀！做咩呀？走失晒喇！》<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190807/59905509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190807%2F59905509&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=cde3602c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190807%2F59905509&h=dae6271c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190807/59905509</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點6：</span></span>8月5日，有手足喺大埔超級城拍片，聽到有防暴以普通話向同行疑似警員講「同志們」。警方記者會聲稱戴住豬咀冇可能聽得清楚佢講咩，但係好多人都聽到係「同志們」(0:38)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CLr4j7tNJjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCLr4j7tNJjE&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ca92a5e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CLr4j7tNJjE</a><br />\n《原來警察之間已經用大陸話溝通》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417770/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417770/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點7：</span></span>8月5日，鄭松泰欲阻止疑似男防暴警對一名女性作出拘捕，講咗立法會議員身份之後仍被諸多阻攔，涉事疑似警員一再強調香港嘅身份證明文件只係得身份證。其後根據熱血時報，該名疑似防暴警提供咗一個警員編號，而該編號查證只係一個輔警，有「有人混入冒警」之嫌。當然，熱血時報提供有關該編號嘅進一步資訊，現時係未有其他佐證。<br />\n<br />\n《發癲要求查鄭松泰身份證 「防暴警」涉提供假編號 》<a href=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-05-2019/54890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F08-05-2019%2F54890&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=8af5a69a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-05-2019/54890</a><br />\n《發癲要求查鄭松泰身份證「防暴警」涉提供假編號!起底組做野》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1412569/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1412569/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/danielleephotography/videos/10220689570054553/?t=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdanielleephotography%2Fvideos%2F10220689570054553%2F%3Ft%3D0&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=3e099216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/danielleephotography/videos/10220689570054553/?t=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點8：</span></span>8月6日起，已經有網絡流傳圖片話有警察要長駐體育館on-call，經查證嗰度為太子警察遊樂會。有人指出有可能係中國執法人員冇地方瞓，所以警察提供地方畀佢地，而睇圖嘅規模同格局，呢點要進一步跟進吓。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y9hLCHD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy9hLCHD.png&h=a3ea5771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《[有圖］原來班狗日日都訓體育館24小時On Call》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1423422/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1423422/page/1</a><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ARgKnD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ARgKnD.jpg&h=0d3d3fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《耆樂警訊 @太子警察遊樂會》<a href=\"https://www.joinmax.com.hk/portfolio_page/%E8%80%86%E6%A8%82%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%8A-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.joinmax.com.hk%2Fportfolio_page%2F%25E8%2580%2586%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=04df30ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.joinmax.com.hk/portfolio_page/%E8%80%86%E6%A8%82%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%8A-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點9：</span></span>8月8日，有手足喺太和站影到有人拖住寫有「武警八六七三部隊」嘅拖喼，查證此部隊隸屬中國武警部隊機動63師（駐山西夏縣）。警方於8月9日記者會純粹指出有武警混入警隊係謠言，但係亦冇進一步解釋或跟進，而一個駐山西武警出現喺香港呢件事已經好奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRPVfut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRPVfut.jpg&h=86da6ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《（突發）太和站見到武警》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1433776/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1433776/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點10：</span></span>8月9日，浸會大學教授Jean-Pierre Cabestan喺法國報紙《Figaro》指出，佢收到消息有識廣東話嘅中國武警混入警隊，而警隊已經絛視港府直接聽北京同中間人嘅指示。有手足提供資料，呢位教授係識中文同普通話嘅中國政治學者，喺中國學術界network唔細，而BU嘅官網都詳細列咗佢喺遠東同中國嘅研究好有成果。關於呢位教授篇文嘅用字，要識法文嘅手足進一步fact check。<br />\n<br />\n《Hongkong: &laquo;La marge de man&oelig;uvre de Xi Jinping est &eacute;troite&raquo;》<a href=\"http://www.lefigaro.fr/international/jean-pierre-cabestan-sur-hongkong-la-marge-de-manoeuvre-de-xi-jinping-est-etroite-20190804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lefigaro.fr%2Finternational%2Fjean-pierre-cabestan-sur-hongkong-la-marge-de-manoeuvre-de-xi-jinping-est-etroite-20190804&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=3cc8b9a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lefigaro.fr/international/jean-pierre-cabestan-sur-hongkong-la-marge-de-manoeuvre-de-xi-jinping-est-etroite-20190804</a><br />\n《大陸武警混入警隊 - 馮睎乾》<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190809/20745422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F20745422&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ca90cd26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F20745422&h=de3361d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190809/20745422</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點11：</span></span>8月10日，蘋果喺大埔嘅live拍低咗同某警員嘅對話，其中一位嘅口音非常有趣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.independence.union/videos/769528613495988/?t=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.independence.union%2Fvideos%2F769528613495988%2F%3Ft%3D0&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=180b626b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.independence.union/videos/769528613495988/?t=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點12：</span></span>8月10日，警方喺尖沙咀清場拉咗個女仔，有手足影到防暴以一個唔常見於香港警察嘅姿勢自衛。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8P3rnaA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8P3rnaA.jpg&h=6043b5ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《武警，扎馬出賣左你自己 曝露左自己身份》"},{"pid":"654ca1d6f6453c9539ffe19d22c7a0ad02e12de5","tid":1472181,"uid":89898,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點13：</span></span>8月11日，北角恐襲期間有為數不少衣著同香港警察相近嘅疑似警員出現，唯根據警察通例，該批人士相信並非原有嘅香港執法人員。而該批疑似警員曾以人牆保護紅衣恐怖分子換衫（留意肩章相信係同一批人），而相信紅衣恐怖分子為大陸人，極有可能係混入警隊嘅武警配合其行動。（部分圖片同第14點重疊）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aP68AvZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaP68AvZ.png&h=6fe1e59a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07k5CKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07k5CKj.png&h=9163a157&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/2458314564236158/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fvideos%2F2458314564236158%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ff56ebb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/2458314564236158/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqNS2aZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcqNS2aZ.jpg&h=19964c0c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點14：</span></span>近日部份前線疑似警員出勤時，身上會配有一舊紅色不知明物體，有人猜疑係作標示非本地執法人員之用。比對近日嘅其他照片，發現可能係頭盔後面嘅一舊零件，但係其功能、扎馬警心口嘅紅色標誌物、點解過往都唔覺有呢舊嘢等疑問尚有待查證。（部分圖片同第13點重疊）<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DF1Mnci.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDF1Mnci.png&h=9a6a96eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wz6c2ch.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwz6c2ch.png&h=1fee8856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZpRyi1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZpRyi1.png&h=ebd31867&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《點解全部支那人樣ge犬都有紅色扣label》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1443767/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1443767/page/3</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點15：</span></span>8月11日，有片段拍到一名示威者被制服在地期間，附近疑似防暴警察以普通話向旁邊嘅記者講「退後一點」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/1977911735643450/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fvideos%2F1977911735643450%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=0733d196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/1977911735643450/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/maxngck/videos/10157404126951870/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmaxngck%2Fvideos%2F10157404126951870%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=9b978202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/maxngck/videos/10157404126951870/</a><br />\n《「核彈」公安扮警話：退後一點！（有片）》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459626/page/1?post=273e6a6009b9a3350d65fb586ce68e1da2b6e138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459626/page/1?post=273e6a6009b9a3350d65fb586ce68e1da2b6e138</a><br />\n《[核彈，一定要推] 同一條片發現公安偽裝黑警，同黑警偽裝示威者既有力罪證。》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1451545/page/1?post=aeb5aaf82b417eab4c34172c658d618611cb409d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1451545/page/1?post=aeb5aaf82b417eab4c34172c658d618611cb409d</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點16：</span></span>8月11日，有黃埔花園居民拍到一班疑似防暴警察擅闖私人地方，情況與8月3日擅闖雅景臺大堂相似，有可能係出於對香港法律嘅唔理解。另外，由片可以聽出部份疑似防暴警口音奇怪（如0:39一句）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1lookchat12/videos/568344553698094/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1lookchat12%2Fvideos%2F568344553698094%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=d8c1c5a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1lookchat12/videos/568344553698094/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點17：</span></span>8月11日，疑似防暴警衝入葵芳地鐵站，於室內放咗不下3發催淚彈，嚴重有違使用原則。而影片所見（0:45），事隔數十秒有一名控疑似防暴警出面制止，以警棍指示其同僚退回室外，可見開槍並非合乎常規及行動計畫，有可能係唔熟香港慣例、唔聽指揮嘅武警所為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KJJChannel/videos/357418328508745/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKJJChannel%2Fvideos%2F357418328508745%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=d80aeaef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KJJChannel/videos/357418328508745/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點18：</span></span>8月11日，有手足睇蘋果喺荃灣嘅live，發現有疑似警察嘅背心後面有中國國旗同軍階標誌，而當時正正係白衣人發動無差別襲擊嘅時間。根據同日北角同721元朗嘅經驗，相信呢批白衣人亦都係有紅色背景，令人懷疑呢班疑似中國警察出現喺現場係為咗協助恐襲。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNFdMEK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNFdMEK.png&h=d52c0e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxyYVD4FjhQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkxyYVD4FjhQ&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=08005c67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxyYVD4FjhQ</a><br />\n《荃灣有隻狗背後有支那國旗同軍階符號？》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1450794/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1450794/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點19：</span></span>8月11日，一名網名「民警小唐」嘅網民喺微博出咗個post，入面嘅相片視角係喺香港警車入面。而該微博曾用「香港同行們」一字，相信係指香港警察，亦間接暗示自己係非香港警察，亦即其網名所示係一名大陸民警，有混入香港警隊執法之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcM1a6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcM1a6w.jpg&h=7066bbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《中國民警係香港警車上影相》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468080/page/1?post=65315ba4116d0c8f3562622323d5dbac2ee64223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468080/page/1?post=65315ba4116d0c8f3562622323d5dbac2ee64223</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點20：</span></span>8 月11日，有手足喺佐敦發現有車牌以ZG為首嘅假救護車，而本地救護車應以A開首，ZG係解放軍救護車。當時尖沙咀正發生警民衝突，呢架車同時出現，令人懷疑係解放軍用以配合警方對傷者嘅拘捕行動，亦有說可能因為混入香港警隊嘅解放軍受傷所致。<br />\n <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7EVfyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7EVfyj.jpg&h=767a06be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbXWKrD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbXWKrD.png&h=add7eca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《(各位小心) 佐敦發現解放軍救護車 同香港救護車極相似 唔好上錯車》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444216/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444216/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑點21：</span></span>8月12-13日，已經不下一次喺機場集會發現有疑似香港警察混入示威者，其後於13日一個疑似公安混入示威者被當場斷正，查證為深圳市公安局福田分局輔警。當然徐錦煬出現喺現場可以係個人原因，可以係獨立於香港警隊嘅間諜行動，但亦有可能係先混入香港警方再假扮示威者放蛇。<br />\n <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZ7LCMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZ7LCMQ.jpg&h=2273e5f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《緊急！機場已有鬼》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1453986/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1453986/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sv09j0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsv09j0a.jpg&h=6a1a36cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ym5Ydj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYm5Ydj9.jpg&h=91867ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haUmVyv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaUmVyv.jpg&h=84f2cba9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《內地公安及警察合作帶備木棍在機場製造騷亂，被現場示威者抓住》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1462882/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1462882/page/1</a><br />\n《【正視聽 】一圖FACT CHECK琴日公安及記者事件》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1471067/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1471067/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其他疑點：</span></span>部份警員長相奇怪一岩一忽，唔止係唔似香港人，有啲係好似師奶大叔咁完全唔似警員（印象中光復元朗見過張圖但係搵唔返）；做嘢完全唔跟香港做法，例如屢次擅闖私人地方、容許男警對女性作出搜身同拘捕等等，當然可能只係警隊失控犯法嘅事例嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">已證偽：</span></span>612當日有一男警顯示編號為9459，於某系統查證顯示是一名女輔警督察。該系統可信性成疑，而輔警編號應該以A作首，所以唔太關事。<br />\n《求驗傳媒》 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/posts/2214812728594930/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkauyim%2Fposts%2F2214812728594930%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=73c51491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/posts/2214812728594930/</a>"},{"pid":"ae313bbf1d5dd43134b7221fec367fac49ef4c38","tid":1472181,"uid":89898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:20:07.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbef1169fc1169d8ff3593561b2438e1dd32e0c","tid":1472181,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgm